{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab in some categories (such as \u8484? with \u8804?; or {\b Ring}), "mono and epi" does not imply "iso"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab in every {\i abelian} category, we have that "iso \u8660? epi and mono" (and though {\b Set} is not abelian, the property still holds)\par}
